{"tid":2228673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"列斯聯最域大波哭喪區","createTime":"2020-10-03T18:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T20:00:01.000Z","uid":12973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87dd30cc230ccf93eb27fda30c8d47181ed8a006","tid":2228673,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:30:59.000Z","msg":"雖然係好睇，諗住曼城實搵到列斯聯逼搶嘅空位啦<br />\n點知冇正前鋒呢下真係自斷雙臀<br />\n每次去到禁區頂都唯有傳返比邊，縮窄哂個角度<br />\n同時對面有人返黎，但左右兩閘都有機會累到 / 唔敢overlap (仲有mendy廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n列斯聯下次對強隊先好繼續買下盤，對中型班反而會老鼠拉龜，同錫菲聯果場都打得辛苦<br />\n呢種打法其實對邊隊都係55波，大家鬥勇鬥體能，中下遊反而唔輸蝕，有時守返列斯聯轉頭仲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n利申：事後孔明包哂頭"},{"pid":"c40d28abd6c1a7ce1425718e453b5e6dc6fa9f40","tid":2228673,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"仲有，丁力我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連半場2.5b都唔比我"},{"pid":"e6e4f1c00e8621e09a1dcf762564639f6f193bad","tid":2228673,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:38:48.000Z","msg":"列斯聯對阿對獌應該大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b197661cee69eeda5ae555df32ec0890cce2bced","tid":2228673,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"列斯聯痛失2分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9004cdd2976aeb284c3c4e21c61ae1c19a2a0d9","tid":2228673,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"有角大點解唔買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a568508a057cb718295c95b515ee2f4ed1935e","tid":2228673,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9004cdd2976aeb284c3c4e21c61ae1c19a2a0d9","tid":2228673,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:40:25.000Z","msg":